@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = paste-admin-access-token-here

### Low-risk transfer using an established beneficiary and trusted device
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions/ingest
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerNumber": "CUST1001",
  "sourceAccountNumber": "ACC1001",
  "destinationAccountNumber": "ACC2002",
  "beneficiaryName": "Priya Sharma",
  "amount": 2500,
  "currency": "INR",
  "transactionType": "TRANSFER",
  "channel": "MOBILE_BANKING",
  "deviceId": "DEVICE-TRUSTED-001",
  "ipAddress": "103.20.44.10",
  "geoLocation": "Pune, India",
  "initiatedAt": "2026-06-22T20:00:00Z"
}

### Expected after asynchronous processing: LOW and APPROVE
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
